Company Overview of Veritas Asset Management LLP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Veritas Asset Management LLP is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to high net worth individuals, institutions, charities, and trusts. It manages separate client focused equity portfolios. The firm also launches and manages equity and balanced mutual funds and hedge funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm employs long-only and long-short strategies while creating its portfolios. It employs fundamental and quantitative analysis along with a combination of top-down with the bottom-up stock picking approaches while making its investments. The firm was founded in 1996 and is based in London, Unit...
Veritas Asset Management LLP is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to high net worth individuals, institutions, charities, and trusts. It manages separate client focused equity portfolios. The firm also launches and manages equity and balanced mutual funds and hedge funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm employs long-only and long-short strategies while creating its portfolios. It employs fundamental and quantitative analysis along with a combination of top-down with the bottom-up stock picking approaches while making its investments. The firm was founded in 1996 and is based in London, United Kingdom with an additional office in Hong Kong. It was formerly known as Veritas Asset Management (UK) Limited. As of October 31, 2014, Veritas Asset Management LLP operates as a subsidiary of Affiliated Managers Group Inc.
